-- Barcelona’s Abidal Recovers After Transplant, Europa Press Says
-- B y   A l e x   D u f f
-- 2012-04-11T12:35:31Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-11/barcelona-s-abidal-recovers-after-transplant-europa-press-says.html
Barcelona defender  Eric Abidal  is
recovering well after a liver transplant yesterday, Europa Press
reported, citing the European soccer champion’s president Sandro
Rosell.  Abidal, 32, had a tumor removed from the organ last year,
and doctors decided last month that a transplant was necessary.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
